NexPoint Multifamily Capital Trust Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















nexpoint multifamily capital trust inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Real Estate
Sub-Industry: REIT
NexPoint Multifamily Capital Trust, Inc. (NMCT) operates as a real estate investment trust. The Company acquires, owns, and develops multi-family properties, as well as provides investment strategy and financial advisory services. NMCT serves customers in the United States.




